![](https://images.squarespace-cdn.com/content/v1/5d56e145f80b7500016ba502/4dce8c87-2744-4078-826a-7d8008b4dca3/Screenshot_20240531_170827.jpg)

Nia Jax opens the show. Nia called out Bayley. Bayley comes out and gets blindsided by Piper and Chelsea.

They threw her in the ring, and beat her up some more, while Nia watched. Nia then got on the microphone and said it didn’t matter who the champion was at SummerSlam, she had an automatic shot, so go right ahead.

* * *

![](https://images.squarespace-cdn.com/content/v1/5d56e145f80b7500016ba502/68d97af2-5cd9-406b-94c4-448ce892911a/20240531_171317.jpg)

AJ Styles tells Nick Aldis he needs to address his future tonight.

* * *

![](https://images.squarespace-cdn.com/content/v1/5d56e145f80b7500016ba502/cb2dea8e-3d15-46dc-82bd-60b8c8343635/Screenshot_20240531_172059.jpg)

*   ## **_TOMASSO CIAMPA DEF. AUSTIN THEORY_**
    

Great match that ends when Grayson Waller costs Theory the match when he was overheard saying Theory only mattered because he’s getting thr Grayson rub.

* * *

![](https://images.squarespace-cdn.com/content/v1/5d56e145f80b7500016ba502/950860e1-4f99-41b4-a05d-743fa48850c5/Screenshot_20240531_173107.jpg)

Naomi asks Nick Aldis to give her and Bayley a match against Piper and Chelsea later tonight. But she interrupted Blair Davenport and Blair did not like that.

LA Knight enters the room looking for Logan Paul

* * *

![](https://images.squarespace-cdn.com/content/v1/5d56e145f80b7500016ba502/798ebe0c-084c-41fb-9cb9-6f7a3089680b/Screenshot_20240531_174010.jpg)

Back from break, LA Knight declares he wants Logan Paul's US Title. Carmelo Hayes walks up and says why would LA want to face… LA?

LA Knight catches the botch and makes sure it doesn’t stay ignored. Melo says if Logan wants a guy who talks the talk, he’ll fight LA. If he wants someone who walks the walk, he’ll come to Melo.

* * *

![](https://images.squarespace-cdn.com/content/v1/5d56e145f80b7500016ba502/5f63fc4c-2384-497b-9d28-4fab4faf1691/Screenshot_20240531_174913.jpg)

*   ## **_ANDRADE DEF. APOLLO CREWS_**
    

Decent match. Andrade picks up a quick victory. Earlier in the night Angel Garza tried to recruit Andrade. Andrade said no thanks but Angel didn’t really get the message. He comes out with the rest of Legado de Phantasma after this match and they all get ignored by Andrade.

* * *

![](https://images.squarespace-cdn.com/content/v1/5d56e145f80b7500016ba502/3a679f0f-af23-4cfe-a8db-39ae0e3d4463/Screenshot_20240531_175228.jpg)

The Bloodline is in the back when Heyman walks up. He says he wants to better serve Solo and the Bloodline but he can’t because they’re being violent for violence sake.

Solo tells Heyman not to worry. “We” have Cody right where we want him. Heyman asks.. With all due respect.. Who is “WE”?

* * *

![](https://images.squarespace-cdn.com/content/v1/5d56e145f80b7500016ba502/c33c978a-581f-4c34-b9b7-45df6774502f/Screenshot_20240531_175944.jpg)

Apollo takes out Angel Ortiz for getting involved in his match with Andrade earlier.

* * *

![](https://images.squarespace-cdn.com/content/v1/5d56e145f80b7500016ba502/c9b5e5dc-5ab2-4281-a2dc-a4228b0d7885/Screenshot_20240531_175958.jpg)

Kevin Owens is disappointed they couldn't make Randy the King of the Ring but he says we all saw Randy didn't really lose. Owens wants to fight the Bloodline.

![](https://images.squarespace-cdn.com/content/v1/5d56e145f80b7500016ba502/e3e45564-bc47-4c97-b7fd-e8eda30af951/Screenshot_20240531_180200.jpg)

Heyman comes out and tells Kevin that when he fought Roman. Roman respected Kevin Owens. But Solo has recruited CRIMINALS into the Bloodline. They don’t respect Kevin at all.

Roman and Heyman used to do background checks because they didn’t want people like this representing the Bloodline. He’s begging Owens not to call out the Bloodline because they are going to do bad things to him.

Kevin doesn’t trust him. He thinks Heyman is pulling the strings behind all of this. Kevin says the Bloodline has done everything to him but he’s still standing and he had a great time!

But that was the Bloodline. Reigns and the Usos, men that Kevin Owens also respects. Solo and those other two guys are NOT the Bloodline. They're just some dudes he doesnt even care to know and he wants them out of the WWE. So he will keep fighting.

Heyman says he is trying to SAVE Kevin Owens. Why won’t he try to understand?! WHY WONT ANYBODY LISTEN TO HIM?! Heyman gets carried away and hits Kevin Owens with the microphone.

![](https://images.squarespace-cdn.com/content/v1/5d56e145f80b7500016ba502/6f587ed8-4020-417a-b016-3bc74b840c96/Screenshot_20240531_180941.jpg)

The Bloodline comes out before Kevin Owens could destroy Heyman. The Street Profits come out to even the odds. They brawl to the commercial break.

* * *

![](https://images.squarespace-cdn.com/content/v1/5d56e145f80b7500016ba502/dc6782c6-af0d-4794-a1d7-2e91f69a777c/Screenshot_20240531_181609.jpg)

*   ## **_BLOODLINE FKA GUERRILLAS OF DESTINY DEF. STREET PROFITS_**
    

Very stiff match. Lots of hard strikes and clotheslines. Match ends when Tama Tonga sneaks a tag and Montez Ford didn’t notice before he finished the wrong wrestler and got finished himself.

* * *

![](https://images.squarespace-cdn.com/content/v1/5d56e145f80b7500016ba502/32972d27-762f-487c-8186-7c2ba6d9d511/Screenshot_20240531_182725.jpg)

Jade and Bianca are talking about heading to RAW to defend the Women’s Tag Team Championships. Indi asks if they’re going to RAW to injure someone the same way they hurt Candice.

Bianca reminds Indi that they targeted Biancas knee first. Jade gets in Indis face and threatens to injure her.

![](https://images.squarespace-cdn.com/content/v1/5d56e145f80b7500016ba502/16aa2a0b-199b-422c-9885-4507b3d09902/Screenshot_20240531_183533.jpg)

*   ## **_CHELSEA GREEN AND PIPER NIVEN DEF. BAYLEY AND NAOMI_**
    

Naomi takes the pin and costs the babyfaces the match here. I wonder how that will come around.

* * *

![](https://images.squarespace-cdn.com/content/v1/5d56e145f80b7500016ba502/2174a5f9-fc1a-4201-a021-4c01fb31dff8/Screenshot_20240531_184559.jpg)

AJ heads to the ring and says goodbye to multiple superstars on his way out.

![](https://images.squarespace-cdn.com/content/v1/5d56e145f80b7500016ba502/5eef7cb4-e0f0-40ed-bce6-b9857939cde1/Screenshot_20240531_185105.jpg)

AJ says he doesn’t have time to wait at the back of the line for a world championship opportunity. Last weekend he got to throw a graduation party for his son and he realized he missed too many of these.

So he’s going to go home and be a phenomenal father.

![](https://images.squarespace-cdn.com/content/v1/5d56e145f80b7500016ba502/daa98361-1049-490c-8cab-bd456cf5b0ed/Screenshot_20240531_185612.jpg)

AJ calls Cody out to the ring to tell him their match at Backlash was one of the best he’s ever had. AJ wants Cody out here because he wants to hand Cody the keys to the HOUSE THAT AJ STYLES BUILT.

Cody says they've only ever had one text exchange between them and it was after Backlash. Cody texted AJ to see if he was OK. Aj responded “I’m good little bro.”

Cody thanks AJ for being the big bro of the locker room.

Then AJ attacks him and Styles Clashes him off the steps to end Smackdown.